  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>This update includes a few minor features and bug fixes.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.7.4.13-TicketImport\">Ticket Import</h3><p>The location\u00a0imported for\u00a0each ticket in a ticket import will now\u00a0be\u00a0set as the ticket location, rather than the location you are logged into when performing the import.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.7.4.13-RepairDeviceReport\">Repair Device Report</h3><p>The following fields were added to the Repair Device Report:</p><ul><li><p>Ticket Assignee</p></li><li><p>Warranty Provider</p></li><li><p>Customer ID</p></li><li><p>Billing Agent ID</p></li><li><p>Billing Agent Company</p></li><li><p>Billing Agent Contact</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.7.4.13-InventoryImportTemplate\">Inventory Import Template</h3><p>The Instock qty will now be filtered by\u00a0the location the user is logged into.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.7.4.13-CatalogItemImport\">Catalog Item Import</h3><p>To help prevent import mistakes, an error will now be\u00a0thrown when a catalog item is imported as serialized, but not inventoried.</p>",
